citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:43 pm on 08-
MAR-23.
The inspectors were at the facility at 1:43 pm. Inspectors knocked on door of house, called and left message, honked
horn of car, spoke with an individual at the facility who stated no one was available for the inspection. Inspectors then left
the facility.
